data.description: This is the one!  Updated 3/2/2 home with a lake view that's zoned for A-rated schools in a low HOA community of only 100 homes. The floor plan features stacked bedrooms and an open kitchen that flows into the family room with views of the lake throughout.  Move in ready with a remodeled kitchen (2023), new flooring and baseboards, fresh paint and newer kitchen appliances. Conveniently located between I95 and the Turnpike, close to shopping and dining, less than 2 miles from the new Publix at Aberdeen Square, minutes from parks and the library, and only 3 miles to Harvey E. Oyer Jr. Park and Boat Ramp.
